column4: when i try to "sudo apt-get install xmms" i got this message: E: Could not get lock /var/lib/dpkg/lock - open (11 Resource temporarily unavailable)
E: Unable to lock the administration directory (/var/lib/dpkg/), is another process using it?
Gyoza: right, had synaptic running, didnt know that... cant find xmms in synaptic though.
